What you need to know:

Sokratis Papastathopoulos was released from his contract this week, while Mesut Ozil is on the brink of a transfer to Turkish club FenerbahceArteta, whose team are FA Cup holders, said the departures had left his squad short in certain areasArteta had stressed several times he was unhappy with the bloated nature of the squad and feels the departures will help him achieve a better balance